roar "=== Rocket Launch Countdown ==="
roar ""

count bind 10

murmur Countdown from 10 to 0
flag bind 1
sniff count >= 0 : sniff flag == 0 : dive
flag bind 0
sniff flag == 0 : roar "T-minus " + count + " seconds..."
sniff flag == 0 : count bind count - 1
flag bind 1
sniff count >= 0 : sniff flag == 1 : soar

